 Tahoma, Arial, Simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; display: inline !important; font: 12px/24px Tahoma, Arial, Simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; float: none; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　皮肤青春解码仪来自独一无二的国际最前沿军工技术、利用雷达电波的准确定位术和无线电波的聚焦术对皮肤进行分层定位，分层聚焦，刺激皮肤细胞胶原蛋白快速新生，焕发胶原细胞的生命力，给皮肤充分供给营养和水，从而修复皱纹、锁住水分，改善肤质、肤色，从根本上解决皮肤青春问题。<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><br style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 12px/24px Tahoma, Arial, Simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; display: inline !important; font: 12px/24px Tahoma, Arial, Simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; float: none; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　祛皱修复程序在面部皱纹以及颌下赘肉处，通过细胞共振技术，刺激真皮层的纤维母细胞源源不断产生每天所需的胶原蛋白，修复断裂的弹力纤维，快速消除深层皱纹，使皮肤保持紧致结实，富有弹性。营养导入程序青春解码仪的离子导入和红外输导的复合导入功能，可以将营养精华分解成水溶性的离子状态并直接导入到皮肤的真皮组织，为皮肤细胞，尤其是真皮层内负责产生胶原蛋白的纤维母细胞100%吸收到补充的营养物质，增强皮肤的生命活力。深层补水修复程序青春解码仪将补充给皮肤的水分电解成离子状态，并通过同极离子相斥的作用，将电解水离子在5秒内直接导入到皮肤的基质层，让内层皮肤细胞真正补充到缺失的水分，为缺水肌肤提供了补水、输水、锁水三部曲护肤概念。无与伦比的神奇功效，凸显传统美容的局限生活美容，产品分子不能到达真皮层，只能起到保护作用，用后依赖性大。而光疗、电疗美容，其能量不能定位、不能分层，带有选择性吸收。而SW皮肤青春解码系统利用雷达电波的准确定位术和无线电波的聚焦术对皮肤进行分层定位，分层聚焦，并达到准确治疗，单次快速补水20-30毫升，收缩毛孔率50-200%，真正用数字证明实力，为您再造健康新鲜皮肤。<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><br style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 12px/24px Tahoma, Arial, Simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; display: inline !important; font: 12px/24px Tahoma, Arial, Simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; float: none; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><br style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 12px/24px Tahoma, Arial, Simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<strong><span style=\"color: #3366ff\"><span style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; display: inline !important; font: 12px/24px Tahoma, Arial, Simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; float: none; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">青春解码仪的八大功效<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></strong><br style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 12px/24px Tahoma, Arial, Simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; display: inline !important; font: 12px/24px Tahoma, Arial, Simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; float: none; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto;