ay: inline !important; font: 12px/24px Tahoma, Arial, Simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; float: none; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　4.紧肤、收缩毛孔；<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><br style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 12px/24px Tahoma, Arial, Simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; display: inline !important; font: 12px/24px Tahoma, Arial, Simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; float: none; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　5.改善暗哑、暗黄皮肤，美白嫩肤；<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><br style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 12px/24px Tahoma, Arial, Simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" />\r\n<span style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; display: inline !important; font: 12px/24px Tahoma, Arial, Simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; float: none; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　6.改善眼袋，祛除黑眼圈，减少眼龄；<span class=\"Apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><br style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font: 12px/24px Tahoma, Arial, Simsun; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; color: rgb(51,51,51); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjus