INSERT INTO `sl_news_data` VALUES('930','<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 2em; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/24px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">YAG激光美容是新一代无痛E光，光能作用于皮肤表皮产生光热解作用和生物刺激作用，实现祛除各类色斑、血丝、脱毛；频率产生的高频电磁波透过表皮作用在真皮层细胞（大量的水分子、极性分子及带电离子）的水分子产生高速震动，通过高速旋转摩擦，而产生热能达到45-60度，发生炎性反应，使胶原蛋白增生、重新排列、数量增加，可达到紧肤、皱纹；光能与射频有效相结合，可穿透表皮到达真皮深层，达到即刻紧肤、长效除皱、祛除真皮斑、轻松抗衰老的目的。避免了光子、彩光在治疗中起泡、色素沉着及返黑现象，而且对治疗真皮斑、除皱等效果显著。</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 12px/24px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.whzhzxmr.com/uploadfile/2014/0210/20140210010827711.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height: 400px\" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 2em; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/24px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　治疗范围：</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 2em; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/24px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　光能：嫩肤、脱毛、毛孔粗大、皮肤粗糙、日晒斑、老年斑、雀斑</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 2em; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/24px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　RF：面部提升、收紧、眼部皱纹、黑眼圈、鼻唇沟皱纹、身体塑型</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 2em; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/24px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　光能+RF：黄褐斑、真皮斑、细小绒毛</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 2em; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/24px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　美容优势：</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 2em; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/24px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">　　新一代无痛E光：光能+射频+表皮冷却技术，解决了真皮斑、除皱、拉皮等的治疗难题，有效祛除浅层细毛；是此领域的一个突破；</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 2em; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding-left: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; padding-right: 0px; font: 14px/24px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 